HOW TO COMPILE UNDER METROMS:

In folder METROMS/apps, execute './build_3.5.bash_new arctic-20km' 
to build roms-3.5 arctic-20km application. To compile in paralell, 
add the keyword '-j 4' after the name of your application to use 
4 cpus in the compilation process. You still need to specify which 
compiler etc you want to use insode the 'build_3.5.bash_new'-file.